{"tid":1893542,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<武漢肺炎> 于非：世衛向 YouTube 施壓  幫中國穩住防疫輿論","createTime":"2020-02-23T10:30:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T12:18:39.000Z","uid":227801,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1c697c908a51284dfdb8e43269d752b105c3e259","tid":1893542,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T10:30:53.000Z","msg":"悶透社gumboringer<br />\n5 小時前 (已編輯)<br />\n【關於 YouTube 黃標的新觀察】<br />\n<br />\n現在謎底基本已經解開，文昭提過大約兩星期前，世衛要求 YouTube 高層處理輿論，以免阻礙中國防疫的信心云云，於是那段日子 YouTube 的審批標準特別苛刻，凡遇上「武漢肺炎」、「疫症」等字詞幾乎自動黃標。<br />\n<br />\n假如 Youtuber 講疫情出片量多，會被進一步標籤整條 Channel 都有問題，列入觀察名單，之後變成任何主題、不講疫情也被黃標，必須按「經YouTube 人手審批」，即使一些片無事，審批完成也是封殺了整整一兩天後的事了。<br />\n<br />\n最近經過試驗，發現只要 Channel 之前講述疫情的片未算太多，未列入觀察名單，再加上網友去信 YouTube 投訴等壓力，YouTube 近日看來稍為放鬆了審查，較新的影片只要不直接寫上「武漢肺炎」等敏感詞，未至於立即黃標，但是，這等於犧牲了讓人們留意疫情的關鍵字，讓搜尋疫情主題的觀眾不輕易看到，miss 了影片，由「硬壓制」變相換成「軟壓制」，令主題減少曝光。<br />\n<br />\n所以，近日現象變成部分 Youtuber 新片，只要不觸及敏感詞終於沒有立即黃標，但流量減了幾成左右。<br />\n<br />\n換句話說，世衛譚德塞為了幫中國穩住防疫輿論，向 YouTube 施壓聲稱為全球好，增強防疫信心、減少陰謀論和謠言，結果亂石擲竹林去封殺，不問內容先Scan 敏感詞再算，接到觀眾控訴才改方法，但仍未回復正常，不愧「用心良苦」。"},{"pid":"9bbc814b0c5a95b8bced446bfdfb29e571479393","tid":1893542,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T10:31:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />google 狗"},{"pid":"23890442290decdfaf544caea4f5a6a2a89d0b91","tid":1893542,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T10:33:26.000Z","msg":"中國模式 輸出全球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15590d0416717ec97de1b0eabf8a7efeebc02944","tid":1893542,"uid":4964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T10:34:16.000Z","msg":"fact check左?如果係真,應該好爆"},{"pid":"c4bd427a57e4e37c742a2f1d06319b0a12d565ba","tid":1893542,"uid":279938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T11:10:25.000Z","msg":"關於WHO 邀請各大社交媒體就遏止「假訊息」問題開會，文昭都係引用以下新聞來源<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2020/02/14/facebook-google-amazon-met-with-who-to-talk-coronavirus-misinformation.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2020%2F02%2F14%2Ffacebook-google-amazon-met-with-who-to-talk-coronavirus-misinformation.html&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAyjC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=c9eabbf5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnbc.com/2020/02/14/facebook-google-amazon-met-with-who-to-talk-coronavirus-misinformation.html</a>"},{"pid":"e0992e7661718f852b7d82b2847b3648f8d66598","tid":1893542,"uid":5103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T12:06:35.000Z","msg":"我地小隊依家正努力整合緊屬於我地香港本土YouTube channel<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴打們可以支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n攻擊重要,防守都好重要<br />\n如果出面做攻擊,我地會做好防守依一個環節<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地都仲有一班本土channel須要我地大力支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">目標對每個本土channel：subscibe+㩒鐘仔+share俾10個fd+睇片+留言+like </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">覺唔覺得香港真係無乜本土YouTube Channel? (2.1)</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1886497\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1886497</a>"},{"pid":"ad6d895e0280578fa634f7fa256512b1c7420899","tid":1893542,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T12:09:56.000Z","msg":"將filter敏感詞模式輸出全世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8156e278efc16a254c696b95a951a21348176ff6","tid":1893542,"uid":68430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T12:18:39.000Z","m